name: Kraken Expands Alpaca Partnership to Boost Global Tokenized Equities Adoption
description: The vast hands of the architecture, forged in oily brass and gleaming chrome, enact the solemn ritual. A token cluster burns at the nexus of the binding covenant, where algorithmic weather dictates the terms of flowing fate across cyan-magenta grids.
